@code{global_variances(x, false)} means that @code{x} is not the data matrix, 
but the covariance matrix, avoiding its recalculation,

@example
(%i1) load (descriptive)$
(%i2) s2 : read_matrix (file_search ("wind.data"))$
(%i3) s : cov1 (s2)$
