@end group
@end example

Function @code{list_correlations} also has an optional logical argument: 
@code{list_correlations(x,true)} tells Maxima that @code{x} is the data matrix, 
making the same as @code{list_correlations(x)}.  On the other hand, 
@code{list_correlations(x,false)} means that @code{x} is not the data matrix, 
but the covariance matrix, avoiding its recalculation.

See also @code{cov} and @code{cov1}.
@end deffn

